<ENAMEX TYPE="LAW">Title 1</ENAMEX> funds <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">each year</TIMEX>. This means that <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">parents</ENAMEX> would receive a voucher worth
not <NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">$1,500</NUMEX> per <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">student</ENAMEX>, but <NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">$313.33</NUMEX>. That doesn't buy a lot of hope, even in
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Goodrich</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Texas</ENAMEX>. In fact, there are no private <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">schools</ENAMEX> in the vicinity, which
