<TIMEX TYPE="DATE">year</TIMEX><NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">,147</NUMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">students</ENAMEX> in the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Houston Independent School District</ENAMEX> qualify to opt out
of failing public <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">schools</ENAMEX> under this program. How many have taken advantage of
